{"department_text": "Accessories", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=2575&name=Batteries&", "text": "Batteries ", "description_title": "Batteries", "parent_url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=1&name=Accessories", "keyword_count": {"batteries": 2}, "description_wc": 81, "description_text": "Sometimes, it is easy to overlook that little component that gives life to your electronic devices: the battery. Batteries give life to all your gadgets. Without a battery, your gadgets are nothing but useless contraptions. Every device, from your cameras to the remote control, needs the power that the electronic battery provides. You can be assured that we carry nearly every battery type\u2014from AA to AAA, to laptop batteries and chargers \u2014 all at a price you can\u2019t be beat!", "parent_text": "Accessories", "keyword_density": {"batteries": "2.5"}, "department_id": 6},
{"department_text": "Accessories", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=3&name=Cables&", "text": "Cables ", "description_title": "PC & Computer Cables", "parent_url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=1&name=Accessories", "keyword_count": {"pc": 2, "cables": 17, "computer": 5, "computer cables": 3}, "description_wc": 183, "description_text": "Your computer cables are one of the most critical components of your desktop or notebook computer. Your cables connect you and your computer to the world, and make it possible for every interaction. Yet your computer cables are often the most overlooked part of your PC. Most users don't know that getting customer computer cables means you can put your PC in a more convenient location, so that you are not trapped by short keyboard cables, and allow your printer to be moved off of your desk and across the room if needed. Custom cables mean you control the layout of your workspace, rather than the length of the original cables. Buying discount cable products from manufacturers like: Cables To Go , Startech Cables , or Ultra Cables , is easier than ever, and we have the most complete selection of custom cables and discount cable products available! So whether you are looking for HDMI Cables , Firewire Cables , USB Cables , Printer Cables , Audio / Video Cables , Power Cords , or Monitor Cables , you will find them here.", "parent_text": "Accessories", "keyword_density": {"pc": "1.2", "computer": "2.9", "cables": "9.8", "computer cables": "3.5"}, "department_id": 6},
