{"level": 0, "url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=79&name=Audio/Video-Cables&", "text": "Audio/Video Cables ", "description_text": "In setting up a great home entertainment system, you will always find the need to make use of an audio video cable or two. Audio video cables are important so you can hear music and see images on the TV screen or monitor. With just a few digital audio cables, you can connect your A/V receiver with your impressive choice of loudspeakers and subwoofer. Home theatre cables are available to connect your speaker system, your video display and DVD/CD player. However, there are also computer audio video cables available for your monitor and peripherals. We us, you will definitely find the biggest collections of audio video cables.", "description_wc": 109, "parent_url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=3&name=Cables", "parent_text": "Cables", "department_text": "Cables", "department_id": 12},
