{"department_text": "Memory", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=36&name=Flash-Memory&", "text": "Flash Memory ", "description_title": "What You Should Know About Flash Memory", "parent_url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=10&name=Memory", "keyword_count": {"memory": 16, "flash": 13, "flash memory": 10}, "description_wc": 286, "description_text": "One of the most important new developments in digital technology recent years is the use of Flash memory, sometimes called \"flash RAM\" to power numerous digital devices. Flash memory is a type of memory that can be erased and reprogrammed in units of memory called blocks. Flash memory gets its name because the microchip is organized so that a section of memory cells are erased in a single action or \"flash.\" Unlike RAM (random-access memory), flash memory can continue to store information in the absence of a power source. This constantly powered memory source is ideal for use in digital cellular phones, digital cameras, LAN switches, PC Cards for notebook computers, digital set-up boxes, embedded controllers, video game cards, MP3 players and other devices. Unlike ROM (read-only memory), you can write to flash memory, making it possible to update the operating system and applications via software. Other advantages of flash memory include its fast access time, compact size and the fact that it has no moving parts. We carry one of the world\u2019s most complete inventories of flash memory products by the industry\u2019s finest manufacturers, including Kingston , Lexar , SanDisk , Ultra , PNY , Crucial , Transcend and A-DATA Technology . We have a huge selection the most common types of flash memory such as CompactFlash , Secure Digital , XD-Picture Card and Micro SD . If you\u2019re looking for flash memory \u2013 and if you have digital devices, there\u2019s a good chance you\u2019ll need it \u2013 we\u2019re your one-stop shop. Because when it comes to flash memory, we have the best selection by the top manufacturers at the very lowest prices.", "parent_text": "Memory", "keyword_density": {"flash memory": "7.3", "flash": "4.7", "memory": "5.8"}, "department_id": 56},
