{"department_text": "Electronics", "level": 0, "url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=2707&name=Housewares&", "text": "Housewares ", "description_title": "Housewares & Appliances", "parent_url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=34&name=Electronics", "keyword_count": {"housewares": 4, "appliances": 3}, "description_wc": 154, "description_text": "Yes, we do have housewares. In fact, as a leading supplier of consumer electronic products, we have some of the best kitchen housewares, appliance, and personal grooming devices available, including electric shavers. We carry products from the leading manufacturers, such as: DirtDevil , Oster , Panasonic , Sunbeam , and many more. From rice cookers, breadmakers, toaster ovens, vacuums, Convection Oven with Rotisserie, Blender, and so much more - we have them all! Remember, electrical appliances don't last forever. If you have appliances and housewares that are several years old in your home, it is time to replace them. Kitchen housewares especially are used heavily and with constantly improving technology, today's appliances perform faster, with less energy, and more safely than ever before. Especially true of electric shavers, where over time they can dull and accumulate harmful bacteria. So industry experts recommend replacing your electric razor every two to three years at most.", "parent_text": "Electronics", "keyword_density": {"housewares": "2.7", "appliances": "2.0"}, "department_id": 38},
