{"department_text": "Fans, Heatsinks & Cooling", "level": 1, "url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=99&name=Fans, Heatsinks & Cooling", "text": "Fans, Heatsinks & Cooling", "department_url": "http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/Category/category_tlc.asp?CatId=99&name=Fans, Heatsinks & Cooling", "description_title": "PC Cooling Products", "keyword_count": {"cooling": 4}, "description_wc": 141, "description_text": "One of the deadliest threats to your personal computer or notebook is heat! Today's processors and video cards use smaller and smaller technologies running at faster and faster speeds. The result is ever greater amounts of waste heat. Without the right kinds of computer cooling , heat can destroy your high speed computer. Ever computers fresh out of the box can benefit from improved case fans and CPU processor fans . By upgrading your computer cooling system you can have cooler systems and dramatically extend the reliable life of your computer. In many cases you can even improve the performance of your computer by cooling - memory and processors can run faster when cool. Manufacturers such as: Kingwin , Cooler Master , ThermalTake , Corsair , and others, make a wide variety of accessories for computer cooling that make cooler systems.", "keyword_density": {"cooling": "3.0"}, "department_id": 33},
